            <lb xml:id="uuid_8d643dd9-8a19-4df1-8519-f4c2386bfbf9"/><note resp="law-firm" type="paratext"><rs ref="#11988" type="person">Kraus</rs> – <rs ref="#37540" type="institution">Sozialdemokrat</rs>
               <lb xml:id="uuid_bfffbbb7-2407-4d3f-873f-4d30edda75be"/>29. NOV. 1934 </note>
         </p>
